# The Spark bridge

## Cheap — just wrap / unwrap (no data movement)

- **Spark DF → Pandas-on-Spark**: `sdf.pandas_api()`
- **Pandas-on-Spark → Spark DF**: `psdf.to_spark()`

## Expensive — ends at real pandas (driver collect)

- `sdf.toPandas()` · `psdf.to_pandas()`

## The rule (again)

- Methods with the lowercase **`pandas`** in the name **move data to the driver** — treat like `collect()`
- Stay in the cheap wrap/unwrap zone; cross to real pandas only for a **small, final** result
